## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Microscope feature, which allows users to deeply analyze specific data points in charts by providing up to six options (depending on plan) to examine user behavior, create annotations, build cohorts, view user streams, analyze user paths, and explore conversion drivers in funnel analysis.

